<div class="row align-items-center">
  <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto">
    <h2 class="center">Want to adopt this pet?</h2></br>
    <div class="text-black center">
      <form class="form-horizontal">
        <%= form_with(model: @contact, method: :post) do |form|%>
        <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.text_field :name, placeholder: 'Name' %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <p class="form-control-static"><%= current_user.email %></p>
        </div>
        <p>We recommend sharing some basic information about you and your lifestyle to help the Pawesome Adoption Group assist you with your pet enquiry. For example: I have children under 5; I have a dog/cat/other pets; I work part time/full-time etc. The more information you provide in your message, the more likely you are to receive a response.</p>
        <div class="form-group">
        <%= form.text_area :message, placeholder: 'Enter message', class: 'forms' %>
        </div>
        <%= form.submit 'Send Enquiry', method: :post, class: 'btn' %>
        <% end %>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
